{
  "texts": [
    "Every supplemental file is processed by one of several table-extractorfunctions, selected based on the file extension.",
    "These extractor functions include support for Excel, CSV, TSV, and inferred separator loading of TXT files, as well as a PDF table extractor based on Tabula-Py.",
    "For each supporting materials table that is extracted, every column in the table is considered.",
    "The extractor function attempts to map all unique strings to gene symbols.",
    "Mapping may be direct, through some synonym, or identifier."
  ]
}